snippet.title: World Stadium 5 (PS1) - Gameplay
snippet.description: A full game of World Stadium 5, a 2001 baseball video game by Namco. An all-star team of parody-named players from Major League Baseball (Randy Johnson, Pedro Martinez, Mark McGwire, etc.) take on the BayStars.
